      "description": "<p>It would appear that we no longer get a notification in our Lobsters inbox for replies to comments or new comments on stories we submitted.</p>\n<p>I remember a similar thing happened a few years ago, and was intentional (the DB side of things was too slow), but that was fixed. Was this intentional or did we hit a regression or is this purely a me problem?</p>\n<p>(Thank you to everyone who makes Lobsters possible. I know the support burden is nonzero and I hate to add to the pile.)</p>\n",
